		<title type="html"><![CDATA[The Sun Sets on Road Trip 2.0]]></title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://www.roadtrip20.com/2007_12_16-the-sun-sets-on-road-trip-20.html" />
		<id>http://www.roadtrip20.com/2007_12_16-the-sun-sets-on-road-trip-20.html</id>
		<updated>2007-12-17T00:04:56Z</updated>
